<manpage>
    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <class>U8StringBuf</class>
    <method> U8StringBuf_&lt;length &gt; </method>

    <description>
        <para> 继承自U8StringBuf的模版类，U8StringBuf继承自<link url="../AStringBuf/structure/AStringBuf.htm">ASringBuf</link>。</para>
        <para>  </para>
        <para> 按UTF-8编码格式构造一个U8StringBuf对象，并指定字符串字符数。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax_nopara>
        <apiname>U8StringBuf_&lt;length &gt;</apiname>
    </syntax_nopara>   
    
    <remarks>
       <para>length长度中不包含'\0'字符。</para>
       <para>值得注意的是：代码中窄串字符的编码是编译器决定的，不一定是UTF8编码。</para>

   </remarks>
<example>
<pre>
U8StringBuf_&lt;20&gt; u8buf;

CConsole::WriteLine(u8buf.GetCapacity()); //20
CConsole::WriteLine(u8buf.GetLength());   //0
CConsole::WriteLine(u8buf.GetAvailableSpace()); //20
</pre>
</example>   



